/emailverification
    emailVerified.ejs: 
        shows the user that their account email is verified, an 'a' tag
        takes the user to login page. that tag's href is dynamically inputted using the 'loginPage' argument.
    verifyEmail.ejs:
        shows the user a veify email page, requests the user to click on the link which is an 'a' tag, that
        tag's href is dynamically inputted using the 'verifyEmailID' argument
/resetpassword
    passresetlinkexpired:
        shows the user that their clicked link has expired.
    enternewpass:
        its a react build; that has password form fields that the user can submit in order to reset their password 